{
 "translations": [
  {
   "offset": 12,
   "len": 37,
   "en": "a wizened old man with a ready smile.",
   "zh": "一位滿臉皺紋、笑容可掬的老者。",
   "note": "DESC"
  },
  {
   "offset": 53,
   "len": 51,
   "en": "\"Good $T, Avatar. For what purpose hast thou come?\"",
   "zh": "「聖者，$T好。汝此來所為何事？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 164,
   "len": 17,
   "en": "\"I am Nicodemus.\"",
   "zh": "「吾乃尼科德慕斯。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 197,
   "len": 29,
   "en": "\"Why, bless me, I work here!\"",
   "zh": "「哎呀，天佑我，吾就在這裡做事！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 229,
   "len": 59,
   "en": "\"I sell @reagents, teach @spells, and craft magic @staves.\"",
   "zh": "「吾販售@reagents（藥材），傳授@spells（法術），並打造魔法@staves（法杖）。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 291,
   "len": 36,
   "en": "\"I also do a little @experimenting.\"",
   "zh": "「吾也做些@experimenting（實驗）。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 338,
   "len": 74,
   "en": "\"Oh, nothing a great adventurer such as yourself would be @interested in.\"",
   "zh": "「哦，沒什麼，像汝這樣的大冒險者不會@interested（感興）趣的。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 423,
   "len": 38,
   "en": "He gets a suspicious look in his eyes.",
   "zh": "他眼中閃過一絲疑惑之色。",
   "note": "action"
  },
  {
   "offset": 464,
   "len": 20,
   "en": "\"Don't be too nosy, ",
   "zh": "「別太愛管閒事，",
   "note": "partial; gender branch follows"
  },
  {
   "offset": 488,
   "len": 8,
   "en": "girlie!\"",
   "zh": "小姑娘！」",
   "note": "female branch"
  },
  {
   "offset": 497,
   "len": 7,
   "en": "sonny!\"",
   "zh": "小子！」",
   "note": "male branch"
  },
  {
   "offset": 515,
   "len": 20,
   "en": "\"Come back anytime!\"",
   "zh": "「隨時歡迎再來！」",
   "note": "bye"
  },
  {
   "offset": 540,
   "len": 38,
   "en": "\"Nope, nope, I won't talk about that!\"",
   "zh": "「不，不，吾不談那件事！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 643,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"But thou hast not a spell@book!\"",
   "zh": "「但汝沒有@book（書）！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 803,
   "len": 35,
   "en": "\"But none of you has a spell@book!\"",
   "zh": "「但汝等無人有@book（書）！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 875,
   "len": 16,
   "en": "\"Which of you?\" ",
   "zh": "「汝等哪一位？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1007,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "\"In which Circle does $Y wish to study?\" ",
   "zh": "「$Y 希望修習第幾環的法術？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1071,
   "len": 51,
   "en": "\"As everybody knows, there are only eight circles.\"",
   "zh": "「眾所周知，法術環共有八環。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1138,
   "len": 52,
   "en": "\"I sense that $Y is only ready for the #1$1 Circle.\"",
   "zh": "「吾感覺 $Y 只適合修習第 #1$1 環。」",
   "note": "#1 = circle number, $1 = ordinal suffix (th/st/nd/rd)"
  },
  {
   "offset": 1193,
   "len": 40,
   "en": "\"But such matters are not my concern...\"",
   "zh": "「但此等事並非吾所關切……」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1270,
   "len": 34,
   "en": "\"I have no spells of that circle.\"",
   "zh": "「吾沒有那一環的法術。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1381,
   "len": 18,
   "en": "\"Which of these?\" ",
   "zh": "「這些中哪一個？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1415,
   "len": 42,
   "en": "\"Perhaps $Y is not ready for this circle.\"",
   "zh": "「或許 $Y 尚未準備好修習這一環。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1499,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"$Y lacks the #5 gold required.\"",
   "zh": "「$Y 缺乏所需的 #5 枚金幣。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1540,
   "len": 40,
   "en": "\"That spell costs #5 gold. Interested?\" ",
   "zh": "「那個法術需 #5 枚金幣。有意購買？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1586,
   "len": 46,
   "en": "$N hands $Y a piece of rune-covered parchment.",
   "zh": "$N 遞給 $Y 一張佈滿符文的羊皮紙。",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1766,
   "len": 16,
   "en": "\"Which of you?\" ",
   "zh": "「汝等哪一位？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1887,
   "len": 18,
   "en": "\"Which of these?\" ",
   "zh": "「這些中哪一個？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1977,
   "len": 26,
   "en": "\"$1 costs #1 per portion.\"",
   "zh": "「$1 每份 #1 枚金幣。」",
   "note": "reagent price"
  },
  {
   "offset": 2006,
   "len": 27,
   "en": "\"How many dost thou want?\" ",
   "zh": "「汝要購買幾份？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2160,
   "len": 19,
   "en": "$N hands $Y the $1.",
   "zh": "$N 遞給 $Y $1。",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2198,
   "len": 30,
   "en": "\"Thou cannot carry that much!\"",
   "zh": "「汝帶不了那麼多！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2231,
   "len": 49,
   "en": "\"I'll give thee #5; thou dost not need the rest.\"",
   "zh": "「吾給汝 #5 份；其餘汝不需要。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2289,
   "len": 27,
   "en": "\"Thou cannot carry any $1!\"",
   "zh": "「汝什麼 $1 都帶不了！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2329,
   "len": 31,
   "en": "\"Thou cannot afford that much!\"",
   "zh": "「汝付不起那麼多！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2363,
   "len": 47,
   "en": "\"I'll give thee #5; thou cannot have the rest.\"",
   "zh": "「吾賣給汝 #5 份；其餘汝付不起。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2419,
   "len": 28,
   "en": "\"Thou cannot afford any $1!\"",
   "zh": "「汝連一份 $1 也付不起！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2535,
   "len": 16,
   "en": "\"Which of you?\" ",
   "zh": "「汝等哪一位？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2611,
   "len": 36,
   "en": "\"But thou cannot carry a spellbook!\"",
   "zh": "「但汝帶不了法術書！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2663,
   "len": 37,
   "en": "\"But thou cannot afford a spellbook!\"",
   "zh": "「但汝買不起法術書！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2706,
   "len": 48,
   "en": "\"A spellbook costs 45 gold pieces. Interested?\" ",
   "zh": "「法術書售價 45 枚金幣。有意購買？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2798,
   "len": 34,
   "en": "\"Perhaps one of thy friends then.\"",
   "zh": "「那或許汝的某位友人？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2855,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"Yes, I make magical yew staves.\"",
   "zh": "「是的，吾製作魔法紫杉法杖。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2891,
   "len": 92,
   "en": "\"If thou knowest the Enchant spell, thou canst lock a spell within the staff for quick use!\"",
   "zh": "「若汝知曉附魔法術，便可將一個法術封印於法杖之中，以備急用！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2986,
   "len": 63,
   "en": "\"A yew staff costs 100 gold pieces, but it's worth twice that!\"",
   "zh": "「紫杉法杖售價 100 枚金幣，但其價值是這的兩倍！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 3052,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"Wouldst thou like to buy one?\" ",
   "zh": "「汝是否有意購買？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 3090,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"Perhaps some other time, then.\"",
   "zh": "「那或許改天再說。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 3210,
   "len": 16,
   "en": "\"Which of you?\" ",
   "zh": "「汝等哪一位？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 3286,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"But thou cannot carry a staff!\"",
   "zh": "「但汝帶不了法杖！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 3334,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"But thou cannot afford a staff!\"",
   "zh": "「但汝買不起法杖！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 3373,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "The old man hands $Y a yew staff.",
   "zh": "老者遞給 $Y 一根紫杉法杖。",
   "note": ""
  },
